1.0.0.name: drupal/selected_and_unselected_values

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.0.0.description: Provides a field formatter for list text field type displaying both selected and unselected values with extra markup and css styles. Uses translated values if Field translation is enabled.

security-coverage.message: Dev releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.
